AI Legal Compliance Assistant

AI-powered legal compliance assistant built using Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG).
The system retrieves relevant sections from labour law documents using semantic search (Sentence Transformers + FAISS) and generates concise summaries using FLAN-T5.
It provides an interactive interface for querying compliance-related information.

Features;
Semantic document retrieval using Sentence Transformers
Vector search using FAISS
Answer generation using FLAN-T5
Source attribution from legal documents
Interactive interface built with Streamlit

Tech Stack;
Python
Sentence Transformers
FAISS
FLAN-T5
Streamlit
HuggingFace Transformers

System Architecture;

User Query
↓
Semantic Retrieval (FAISS + Sentence Transformers)
↓
Relevant Context Extraction
↓
FLAN-T5 Summarization
↓
Generated Compliance Answer
